                            <SubtypeName>Datapad</SubtypeName>
                            <Name>[ Willow Simmons ]---[ PDA 1/1 ]</Name>
                            <Data>[ Notes ]-[ Such a Waste of Time ]

I’m sick and tired of people arguing about Clang with a “c” or Klang with a “k”!

Who cares!

All that matters is that Clang exists, right?

-Willow Simmons
General Laborer
R.O.S. Industries

P.S.

Having said that, Clang with a “c” just makes more sense.</Data>
